invoke.texi (Code Gen Options): Fix abbreviation typo.

2007-01-30  Ralf Wildenhues  <Ralf.Wildenhues@gmx.de>

	* invoke.texi (Code Gen Options): Fix abbreviation typo.
	* intrinsic.texi (ACCESS, LSHIFT, RSHIFT): Fix typos.
